name: EPS Series Vol. 3: Come and Kiss Me: Tomomi Tsunoda
overview: Tomomi Tsunoda - Come and Kiss Me is the third disc in the EPS music series made by Antinos Records that features: - Photo: Browse through three different photo galleries - CD Player: Play the 2 sides of the single with the songs "Come and Kiss Me", "Make Love in Dark" and the remix of "Come and Kiss Me Flying in Jamaica Mix". - Video Editor: Edit the video with the game video editor. - Video Player: Play the song's video
